Scenario: Seller post ad. 
"Given that I am a seller on the website
I want to be able to add an image for the ad and link it to an available product.
When I open the section to post an ad
Using the upload button to upload the image
Then select an available product to link it to the ad.
Finally, Select preview.
- Success Case:
When I click on the ad, I'll be directed to the product page.

- Failure Case:
When I click on the ad, noting happen or get directed to the wrong product.
